Count 2 - PTC Possess THC with Intent to Deliver - No contest plea.  Convicted.
Count 3 - PTC Possess Methamphetamine - No contest plea.  Convicted.
State moves to dismiss and read in Counts 1 and 4.  Motion granted.
Sentences are withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years concurrent.  Conditions of probation:
1) AODA assessment and follow through; 
2) Random drug screens defendant pays for; 
3) Full-time work or school or combination;
4) COMPAS assessment and follow through;
5) On Count 2, provide a DNA sample;
6) On Count 2, sixty (60) days Manitowoc County Jail, under the Huber Law, commencing 05-12-16 by 6:00 p.m.  Transfer to Dane County Jail is authorized provided defendant not be released on electronic monitoring;
7) Pay costs of the action; and
8) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Defendant is entitled to 1 day jail credit should defendant be revoked.
Minutes.
